Why it is committed here
------------------------
`Report::Formatters::HtmlFormatter` inlines this file verbatim into the single
self-contained `--format html` report so the report works fully OFFLINE — no
CDN, no <script src="http…">, no network at view time. It is a runtime
dependency of the formatter, NOT a secret, so it IS committed (unlike the
generated report.html, which contains real symbols and is gitignored).

Upgrading
---------
Re-fetch the pinned minified build from the source URL above, re-add the one-
line provenance header at the top of cytoscape.min.js, bump the version here,
and confirm the file is the real library (size > 200 KB, contains "cytoscape").

